---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Darko Kuzmanovic — builder of coding-agent tools, terminal utilities, and small software projects."
>
  <h1 class="text-lg text-ctp-mauve mb-6">
    ░&nbsp; ABOUT
  </h1>

  <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-ctp-subtext0 max-w-xl">
    <p>
      I am Darko Kuzmanovic. I build software — mostly late at night, mostly
      for myself, my work, or small communities. Recently that has meant
      tooling for coding agents: extensions for Pi, terminal utilities,
      orchestration helpers, and the occasional small app.
    </p>
    <p>
      Most of what I built over the years stayed private. More of it is public
      now, and this site is where I collect the work and write down what I
      learn along the way.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-sm text-ctp-mauve mt-10 mb-4">
    ░&nbsp; THIS SITE
  </h2>
  <p class="text-sm text-ctp-subtext0 max-w-xl">
    A deliberately small static site, built with Astro and set in Departure
    Mono over Catppuccin Mocha. The source is on
    <a
      href="https://github.com/DarkoKuzmanovic/quz.ma"
      class="text-ctp-green hover:text-ctp-mauve transition-colors"
    >GitHub</a>.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-sm text-ctp-mauve mt-10 mb-4">
    ░&nbsp; SETUP
  </h2>
  <ul class="text-sm text-ctp-subtext0 max-w-xl space-y-2">
    <li><span class="text-ctp-overlay0">Editor —</span> VS Code Insiders, occasionally Zed</li>
    <li><span class="text-ctp-overlay0">Terminal —</span> WezTerm, Konsole</li>
    <li><span class="text-ctp-overlay0">OS —</span> EndeavourOS with KDE Plasma</li>
    <li><span class="text-ctp-overlay0">Machine —</span> Ryzen 5 3600, RX 580, 32 GB RAM</li>
  </ul>
</BaseLayout>
